  - type: software
    title: 'Gemini 3.5 — reactive tiebreak AI agent'
    notes: >-
      Non-author contributor (DataCite contributorType "Other"): reactive
      tiebreak / orthogonal bug-finder engaged when the primary models had
      both failed on the same defect.
    authors:
